data.description: Come view this amazing home located in the very desirable community "The Farm" in Wildomar, CA.   Property features include 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, laminate flooring throughout home, spacious open floor plan, large master bedroom with his and her closets.  Property has other great features such as a NEW ROOF, NEW Heating and AC units, and is in a great family community.   Community features include 3 pools, 3 parks, 3 fishing ponds, hiking trails, tennis courts, basket ball courts, Community RV parking(for additional fee), community gardens, monthly community events, Christmas light competitions, 4th of July parades, and so much more...This property will qualify for all types of financing including FHA, VA, CONV.
